  "remarks": "GBi.009 Designation: a) Lieutenant-colonel b) Spokesperson of the “Military Command”. Passport no: SA000417, issued on 29 Oct. 2003, issued in Guinea-Bissau (Expiration date 10 Mar. 2013). Other information: Naualna was listed on 18 May 2012 pursuant to paragraph 4 of resolution 2048 (2012) as “Spokesperson of the “Military Command” which has assumed responsibility for the coup d’état of 12 April 2012.” Father’s name is Samba Naualna; Mother’s name is In-Uasne Nanfafe.; Listing: Listed by 2048 Committee on 18 May 2025",
